{"tid":585873,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"加州計劃設立「維修權法案」要求廠商開放維修工具","createTime":"2018-03-09T05:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T07:09:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1d4db6e85e6232b25c76af41902ff13a3d34fb13","tid":585873,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"藍骨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在的電子產品大多都難以自行維修，原廠維修雖然質素有保證但所費不菲。最近美國加州就打算設立「維修權法案」，規定廠商需要提供維修資訊和工具，不得強迫用家到原廠維修。 <br />\n<br />\n據加州議會成員 Susan Talamantes Eggman 表示，現時他們已經計劃加入這個法案，通過之後廠商需要提供產品的維修資訊、替換零件和分析工具給消費者和獨立維修店，而不一定需要到原廠維修。加州本身對於產品維修方面的法例已經頗爲嚴格，例如民事法例 1793.02 就規定公司必須在產品推出後 7 年內都提供維修零件，確保舊產品同樣可以獲得維修。<br />\n這個法例在美國早就有大量討論，例如 iFixit 等維修店都強烈提倡這個法例的實施，認爲可以讓用家自行維修手上的電子產品，除了可以減輕維修的成本之外，亦可以減少因為維修成本太高而丟棄產品造成的浪費。不過 Apple 就反對這個法律，表示如果開放維修權，則可能會帶來保安上的隱憂，令不法之徒有機可乘。"},{"pid":"c1cafd54db1f247a56132784301697ba88fc07c9","tid":585873,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:02:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/03/09/california-right-to-repair-bill/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2Fcalifornia-right-to-repair-bill%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=gyCP5LXbMBRKp12G2vGD8LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6f92a6b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/03/09/california-right-to-repair-bill/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"5ae028f729ca0ae57c2f9392524d071862c7abb8","tid":585873,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4700e382868a86994eef30bcc15ca23744d92c9c","tid":585873,"uid":23953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:14:07.000Z","msg":"晒氣啦，就算開放左，依家手機一樣好難維修<br />\n用維修工具有九成機會一打開睇就要換晒其他零件，例如玻璃，moon，鏡頭<br />\n又或者個維修工具成本貴到回唔到本"},{"pid":"8dff8a31647f6c6259c291e853caaff815ccba06","tid":585873,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4700e382868a86994eef30bcc15ca23744d92c9c","tid":585873,"uid":23953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:14:07.000Z","msg":"晒氣啦，就算開放左，依家手機一樣好難維修<br />\n用維修工具有九成機會一打開睇就要換晒其他零件，例如玻璃，moon，鏡頭<br />\n又或者個維修工具成本貴到回唔到本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:43:42.000Z","msg":"將來部部機整到essential phone 咁樣勁難拆既話，大家可以一鑊熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92843d668e49d61e0f16c1b01f1348b25f3a8267","tid":585873,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:02:11.000Z","msg":"又係D左膠法例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091c42be039f06465df22d573f7163b925ef3278","tid":585873,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92843d668e49d61e0f16c1b01f1348b25f3a8267","tid":585873,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:02:11.000Z","msg":"又係D左膠法例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:04:25.000Z","msg":"加州係美國最大左膠州黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2c0517a41509a8f1d5471330da3ceaff8c6831","tid":585873,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92843d668e49d61e0f16c1b01f1348b25f3a8267","tid":585873,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:02:11.000Z","msg":"又係D左膠法例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:09:44.000Z","msg":"關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}